A set of test for the data package manager and authorization/authentication.

Prerequisites: ruby 1.9, bundler, sqlite3

Modify the host variable in features/support/env.rb to point to your computer

Create a passwords.yaml file with the string

     password: my_password

Then:

  - git clone https://github.com/kf8a/tiger
  - cd tiger
  - bundle
  - cucumber
  - enjoy sweet success or crushing failure
